Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:55.54,TITLE1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(463,500)}来自深渊的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 很令人怀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我记得的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 真的是基尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许在这里死了还要好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护主人本应该是我的职责的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 不想再次留下那种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易找回来的东西 又要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度失去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多尔达的丝线 难道断了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾 这次到此就谢幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我写的剧本不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待下次的舞台吧 奥兹·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气息完全消失了 好像真的走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 我怎么可能想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我 要是我停不下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得你会停下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的是基尔的话 绝对会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不相信所谓的『绝对』的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也就相信这么一次 有什么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也绝对不会让人伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我相信你所说的『绝对』啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是你曾经认识的基尔巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫基尔巴·奈特雷依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贝萨流士家族是水火不容的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我 已经成为四大公爵之一 奈特雷依的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不要再像以前那样对我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 那家伙在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 这完全没有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 他可是比谁都重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多机会可以告诉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也清楚他总有一天会明白真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我还是无法说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 真是不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还有别的敌人 快点回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10年了 这儿还是没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 来帮你包扎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 把围巾给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你还有爱妲三个人在屋子里探险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途就掉进这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吗 基尔巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 总算是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 真的是令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来对我来说 这就是最近的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你一直都不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想让你知道我已经改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你还是和以前一样逊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你变了 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得比我高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会开枪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了10年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了各种各样的事会变也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上最重要的东西都还在 并没有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我睡醒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你第一个出现在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有刚才 你还是信守了『绝对』的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什么地方变得不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是现在 我也相信你说的那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 我都会留在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后不管时光怎样流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算两个人的立场改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成为公爵家的人那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实贝萨流士家族和奈特雷依家族的关系不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过是成为贵族罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我会放你走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 还是那副嚣张的德性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是背叛了贝萨流士家族的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是这样 你还是愿意原谅我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 如果你希望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想永远做你的侍仆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是现在也想成为你的侍仆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 基尔巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 和我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦 不要和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的阿嵬茨的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你是爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你是爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字不是叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,染血黑兔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色好苍白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑鸦怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在坟墓前面等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我们是准备去调查那个坟墓的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果爱丽丝不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 难道是因为我把你一个人留下而在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太狠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴 你个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个跟班的 竟敢丢下我一个人搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福 我做了个恶心的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有问清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝对这里也不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一起来的话 多少或许会有些认识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想先整理下思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从阿嵬茨逃出来 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔也会再次回到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有很多事情都觉得如同幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔 怎么样 发现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少如果知道是谁的坟墓就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为声音很微弱 所以一直没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在里边 一直在等我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是白痴兔子的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不听话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷跟着我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在爱丽丝的记忆里出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意识 在看着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的空间开始崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可要好好保护他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 阿嵬茨的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 阿嵬茨好像就是他制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉和巴司卡瓦一直搜寻的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 那只兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那恐怕只是他的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直都在等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来接我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备了好多人偶 我们来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起聊天聊到睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 可爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你能不能放开爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是灵魂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会把你杀掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会让你妨碍他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对她根本就一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么想要陪在她身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和爱丽丝待在一块的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 连自己都不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道为什么会来到这个世界上的臭小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还出手把你抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来到这个世上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来到这个世上 就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊 你就把她抛弃得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不了解爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我就是无法弃她于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得她哪里和我很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 非她不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是没有根据的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是相信自己的真理罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  和你没有半句话投机的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的邀请 不过很不巧
